casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Fateen Rohn MUHAMMAD, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158116
COA: 339157 Supreme Court of Michigan. March 5, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the June 28, 2018 judgment of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court. The motion for evidentiary hearing is DENIED.
